<div class="game_area_description" id="game_area_description">
 <h2>
  About This Game
 </h2>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <img class="bb_img" height="80" src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/cbb10ed198bb0368d299cd92cdacd279.avif" width="780"/>
  </span>
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Step into the thrilling era of the Crusades and forge your destiny in
  <i>
   Knights of the Crusades
  </i>
  . Combining real-time strategy, city-building, and sandbox gameplay, this immersive experience lets you rewrite history and lead a knightly order to glory. Will you rise as a beacon of faith, or succumb to the challenges of a war-torn world?
 </p>
 <h2 class="bb_tag">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video autoplay="" class="bb_img" height="316" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/e81d2a653839db92258b847202c0569a.poster.avif?t=1757184290" width="780">
    <source src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/e81d2a653839db92258b847202c0569a.webm?t=1757184290" type="video/webm; codecs=vp9"/>
    <source src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/e81d2a653839db92258b847202c0569a.mp4?t=1757184290" type="video/mp4"/>
   </video>
  </span>
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <img class="bb_img" height="100" src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/63ae5d92f02e321d148521cfc054b0a0.avif" width="780"/>
  </span>
 </h2>
 <ul class="bb_ul">
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    Begin your adventure as a founding member of the legendary Templars or your custom Holy Order
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    Travel from Western Europe to the Holy Land to take part in the First Crusades
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    Become a founding father of the Holy Order
   </p>
  </li>
 </ul>
 <h2 class="bb_tag">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <img class="bb_img" height="100" src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/b461832b59a79ef48b43ae6913ec61f5.avif" width="780"/>
  </span>
 </h2>
 <ul class="bb_ul">
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    Capture and develop hamlets with dozens of essential structures
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    Navigate complex economy system with survival elements both in RTS and World Map modes
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    Generate resources like silver and piety, which are critical for expanding your influence and sustaining your armies.
   </p>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
   </p>
  </li>
 </ul>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video autoplay="" class="bb_img" height="316" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/59d6ed395b70d37a47ff31026b938367.poster.avif?t=1757184290" width="780">
    <source src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/59d6ed395b70d37a47ff31026b938367.webm?t=1757184290" type="video/webm; codecs=vp9"/>
    <source src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/59d6ed395b70d37a47ff31026b938367.mp4?t=1757184290" type="video/mp4"/>
   </video>
  </span>
 </p>
 <h2 class="bb_tag">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <img class="bb_img" height="100" src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/e99f626d13d3e40fec2848e7975f65df.avif" width="780"/>
  </span>
 </h2>
 <ul class="bb_ul">
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    Engage in epic RTS combat against AI armies on land and at sea.
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    Defend your hamlets, siege massive cities, and rewrite history through challenging scripted scenarios.
   </p>
  </li>
 </ul>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video autoplay="" class="bb_img" height="316" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/7e188432f7d14aefc6de6cbe97f0da1e.poster.avif?t=1757184290" width="780">
    <source src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/7e188432f7d14aefc6de6cbe97f0da1e.webm?t=1757184290" type="video/webm; codecs=vp9"/>
