   </video>
  </span>
 </p>
 <h2 class="bb_tag">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <img class="bb_img" height="100" src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/1b9c6f9957c435e844c78c5ba6243274.avif" width="780"/>
  </span>
 </h2>
 <ul class="bb_ul">
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    Transition into open-ended gameplay after the main campaign, capturing new territories and building alliances
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    Experience escalating challenges with Muslim, Slavic, and Christian AI factions vying for control of key regions
   </p>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
   </p>
  </li>
 </ul>
 <h2 class="bb_tag">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <img class="bb_img" height="80" src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/55db64aa53e91ccca3c86a0b2af63eed.avif" width="780"/>
  </span>
 </h2>
 <ul class="bb_ul">
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    Lead campaigns in the Holy Land, Spain, North Africa, and Eastern Europe. Use strategy and diplomacy to secure alliances or crush your foes.
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    Participate in historical events, like the Reconquista or the defense of Edessa, and determine the fate of the Holy Land.
   </p>
  </li>
 </ul>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video autoplay="" class="bb_img" height="316" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/ef6279c97e82a476a81d6f53615ab44f.poster.avif?t=1757184290" width="780">
    <source src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/ef6279c97e82a476a81d6f53615ab44f.webm?t=1757184290" type="video/webm; codecs=vp9"/>
    <source src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/ef6279c97e82a476a81d6f53615ab44f.mp4?t=1757184290" type="video/mp4"/>
   </video>
  </span>
 </p>
 <h2 class="bb_tag">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <img class="bb_img" height="100" src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/9af7e61b7aee814be1e4c7d2d884fef5.avif" width="780"/>
  </span>
 </h2>
 <ul class="bb_ul">
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    Explore a massive map filled with towns, cities, and pilgrim routes.
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    Navigate dynamic events, including naval battles, sieges, and AI faction wars.
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    Face challenges such as piety-driven resource systems, excommunication events, and escalating enemy attacks.
   </p>
  </li>
 </ul>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  <span class="bb_img_ctn">
   <video autoplay="" class="bb_img" height="316" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" poster="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/53d0f754b9220383db8832894ea73b0f.poster.avif?t=1757184290" width="780">
    <source src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/53d0f754b9220383db8832894ea73b0f.webm?t=1757184290" type="video/webm; codecs=vp9"/>
    <source src="https://shared.fastly.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440120/extras/53d0f754b9220383db8832894ea73b0f.mp4?t=1757184290" type="video/mp4"/>
   </video>
  </span>
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
 </p>
 <p class="bb_paragraph">
  Will you rise to the challenge, expand your knightly order, and safeguard the future of Christendom?
  <i>
   Knights of the Crusades
  </i>
  invites you to embark on a grand journey of strategy, faith, and conquest.
 </p>
